edu.ncsu.csc.utilities

Class DiffSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc.utilities.DiffSession

  • public class DiffSession
extends java.lang.Object
    Responsible for maintaining the session data while the application is processing commit data. This class holds any parsed data until the session is over, at which time it formats said data for output.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Chris Storud (clstroud@ncsu.edu)
